2. data structure and data flow is the most significant and practical problem .
3. we think that the vital steps just a few and concise .
4. we think that the flow chains (net will be better in the context) of the data is continuous ,the same as it's produced and erased.  
   //on the flow  
5. the project usually contains various hierarchies, so horizontal and vertical direction should be both consider and connected .
   //on the structure 
   
6.we have ample examples and structures in our daily life ,we need to learn the different things(structure) in our daily life and 
  develop our ability of converting and connecting the structure which are different in surfaces ,however,same in essence. 
